      "rationale": "At MRL 2 for a Class II device, separate characterization of numerical solver error beyond the code verification and discretization error factors is not required. The solver error contribution is implicitly bounded by the GCI study (factor: Discretization error) and the order-of-accuracy benchmark (factor: Numerical code verification). Scoping out is consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2."
