      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, hemolysis damage model form) is scoped out at MRL 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model and Giersiepen hemolysis model are the accepted standard choices for this class of problem per FDA and literature precedent. A formal model form uncertainty study is not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3."
